						<p>
							Would there be a "Katie &amp; Joe" without Kaitlin? Luckily I’ll never have to know. My biggest advocate before she even met me, Kaitlin has been Joe’s advice-gal and bestie since before I even called California "home".  She quickly went from "Joe’s friend" to one of my own as as we discovered that we were two Harry Potter loving, reality TV watching, bad joke laughing, birds of a feather. I always joke that the biggest perk of being with Joe, is getting Kaitlin too. You know those jokes that are actually serious, and not jokes at all.. well... that could be one of those jokes.
						</p>
